{
  "stem": "13817.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next area would be they would give you a pair of shoes, so-called shoes, which was a wooden sole with a canvas top over it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you would get two rags about 12 by 12 as-- you would wrap them around your feet as-- as stockings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then the next area you would go, you would get two strips with a-- with a number on it, which would be your prison number.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then the next-- the next area, there would somebody stand and grab your arm and put your-- tattoo your number on you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just grab your arm and somebody just starts writing your number on there and it hurts a lot, just-- just one after the other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after that, you would be out there and then you would exchange your uniform.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would give you a needle and some thread, and you would put your number also on your jacket and your pants.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now this whole procedure like I described it to you took two nights and three days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You would be standing there naked more or less all the time, in the fall and up in Auschwitz, where it gets quite cold too.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but no food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody would care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just would count you every few minutes that everybody is there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after that, you would-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] after that, we were put into quarantine, so-called quarantine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The quarantine was run by the kapos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The kapos were-- in the quarantine were all criminals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would do whatever the Nazis told them, the SS.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You never saw one without a whip.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They would whip you for no reason at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
